1
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:01,560
She must've gotten pregnant by some wild man.

2
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:03,560
Yeah, absolutely shameless.

3
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:05,960
So she is that kind of person!

4
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:22,039
A bastard with no known father.

5
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:23,680
Exactly.

6
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:25,200
Just a mongrel.

7
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,810
Everyone is livelier today

8
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:36,050
than when applauding for my shows.

9
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:39,440
You mock the child in her belly as a bastard,

10
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,240
but this child's surname is Yun.

11
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:46,520
It is the child I, Yun Feiyan, begged the Patriarch for,

12
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:49,320
my own flesh and blood to cherish.

13
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,960
How could the surname be Yun?

14
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,090
Don't be afraid.

15
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,120
I'm here.

16
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,260
Before my master passed away,

17
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,400
I swore an oath on his banners.

18
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:06,080
From then on,

19
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:08,580
as long as one person listens to my opera,

20
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:11,970
I will keep the opera disciples safe for that day.

21
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,640
Today, that oath changes.

22
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,760
From now on,

23
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:20,240
as long as I, Yun Feiyan, have a breath left,

24
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,620
I will be the banner for you and the child.

25
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,970
On the day the child is born,

26
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,250
those of you who like to gossip,

27
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,600
feel free to come.

28
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:41,320
My Laixian Opera House

29
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,640
will be free for three days,

30
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,200
so you can listen to your heart's content.

31
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,079
When the time comes,

32
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:47,079
I want everyone in Shanghai to know,

33
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:50,520
that the child Jin Guizhi bears

34
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,780
is my, Yun Feiyan's, own flesh and blood.

35
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,540
Is it really Boss Yun's child?

36
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,800
She must be

37
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,860
the child Boss Yun adopted back then.

38
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,700
Boss Yun is willing to do this.

39
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:19,400
It seems Jin Guizhi and Yun Feiyan

40
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,600
share a special bond.

41
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,040
Boss Yun did this.

42
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,079
Is it possible

43
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:25,400
it was to give Jin Guizhi an alibi?

44
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,120
Then Jin Guizhi,

45
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,800
for Yun Feiyan,

46
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:31,400
killed Xiaotangchun.

47
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,120
It makes sense.

48
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,320
What Jade Rabbit?

49
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,520
More like a bastard looking for a daddy.

50
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,760
Boss Yun is a woman.

51
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,079
That little bitch.

52
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:43,360
Probably spawned on Fourth Road

53
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,079
by some stray man.

54
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:45,720
Right.

55
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:48,079
You bastard!

56
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,520
Get off the stage!

57
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,160
Endure it.

58
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,380
Finish watching the show.

59
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:57,320
Why did you stop singing?

60
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,400
Get off the stage!

61
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,040
She's not singing.

62
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,040
Let's go.

63
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,520
Let's go.

64
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,320
Boring.

65
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,800
Let's move.

66
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,560
What is going on?

67
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,960
It opened again.

68
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,000
Boss Jin.

69
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,860
Didn't you all want to check the family tree?

70
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,320
Come.

71
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:32,850
No need to guess.

72
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,720
On July 7th, 16 years ago,

73
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,720
in the alley behind Shikumen,

74
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:42,240
two opium addicts caught me and humiliated me in an opium den.

75
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:42,700
This...

76
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,930
was burned with their opium pipes.

77
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:49,040
Does it look familiar to you?

78
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,780
Some of you here

79
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,840
were there that night.

80
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:53,800
Let me go!

81
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,400
Madam!

82
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,159
Madam!

83
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,360
Madam!

84
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:58,680
Come here, you.

85
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,540
Help me, Madam!

86
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,000
Separated by only a door.

87
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:04,100
The ladies and gentlemen in the lane.

88
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,760
Do you remember how you left me to die

89
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:08,760
and pushed me into this living hell?

90
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:13,920
It's been days.

91
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,360
I'm going crazy.

92
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,080
It was so dark that night.

93
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:24,120
Who could you see?

94
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,160
Boss Yun saved me back then.

95
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,560
Today,

96
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,159
I will clear her name.

97
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:42,800
Boss Yun,

98
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,420
you took my father's place back then.

99
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:46,640
Today,

100
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,840
I restore your status as my mother.

101
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:49,960
From now on,

102
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:52,720
Jin Fengming is the daughter of Yun Feiyan.

103
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,760
Back on stage,

104
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,680
did I scare you two?

105
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,160
Not at all.

106
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:13,240
Those people are full of hypocritical morals.

107
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:16,400
It's actually like setting off firecrackers in a latrine.

108
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,730
It creates a huge stink.

109
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:18,880
Please sit.

110
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:20,610
That is called moral coercion.

111
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,330
But it means the same thing.

112
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,760
These candied fruits are a bit dry.

113
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:25,020
I'll go get fresh ones.

114
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:26,880
Don't bother.

115
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:30,800
That

116
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,240
is Boss Yun's phoenix crown, isn't it?

117
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,900
That is the phoenix crown from Boss Yun's debut.

118
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:38,040
He was performing the same piece as today,

119
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,500
"The Drunken Concubine".

120
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,280
Today, Boss Jin

121
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,320
and Young Boss Jin

122
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,000
sang quite well,

123
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,920
but the crowd down there ruined it.

124
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:50,960
What a shame.

125
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,720
Boss Yun is gone.

126
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:57,770
I knew this day would come sooner or later.

127
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,600
But Fengming is all grown up now.

128
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,640
It's time he knew.

129
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,920
You didn't come today

130
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:05,080
just to listen to the opera, did you?

131
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,900
We've been looking into the Xiaotangchun case.

132
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,280
Someone told us

133
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:12,040
that a few days before Xiaotangchun's incident,

134
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,440
she said she saw Boss Yun.

135
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,420
What kind of nonsense is that?

136
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,240
Those who want to see her can't,

137
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,280
yet she did?

138
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,970
On the day Xiaotangchun and Meng San were killed,

139
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,440
someone heard singing coming from her house.

140
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,600
We suspect

141
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,850
that Boss Yun might still be alive.

142
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:34,700
When was the last time you saw her?

143
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:37,300
If Boss Yun is still alive,

144
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:40,000
why hasn't she come to see me?

145
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,480
To you,

146
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,320
she must be someone very important.

147
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,600
I was sold to the opera troupe at six.

148
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,960
From then on, I had no family.

149
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,680
Back then, all-female operas were looked down upon.

150
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,120
Xiaotangchun, put more effort into it.

151
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,380
Senior Sister, catch.

152
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:03,020
I muddled through my training for years,

153
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,490
but never really got the hang of it.

154
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:08,640
Until that day.

155
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:12,160
A newcomer arrived at the troupe next door.

156
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,290
That voice coming over the wall

157
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,640
sounded like a golden oriole taking flight.

158
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,240
Are you looking for this?

159
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:38,280
Was that you singing just now?

160
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,679
Sing another line for me.

161
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,240
Right here,

162
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,760
it was torn badly.

163
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:01,680
She got a severe beating from the troupe leader when she got back.

164
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,960
She didn't say a word.

165
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,040
She just took it.

166
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:08,360
You mean,

167
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,530
the junior sister with you was Xiao Tangchun?

168
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,640
Yes.

169
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:15,920
She joined the troupe a few months after me.

170
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,480
When did she find out Boss Yun is a woman?

171
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,240
I don't know.

172
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:25,000
I swore to Boss Yun

173
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,490
that I would never tell anyone.

174
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:29,960
Get away.

175
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,240
Get away.

176
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,400
Let go of me.

177
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:35,520
Get lost.

178
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:37,320
Watch out, or I'll get serious.

179
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,240
Let's go.

180
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,840
Don't actually hurt anyone.

181
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,960
Get lost.

182
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,980
Boss Yun took the blame for me.

183
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,920
Their troupe leader lost money,

184
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:54,050
and was in a bad mood.

185
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:56,040
He made her kneel in the snow

186
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,160
for a whole day and night.

187
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:58,280
Don't scare me.

188
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,520
If your legs are ruined,

189
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:01,650
you'll never be able to perform again.

190
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,360
Feiyan.

191
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:26,440
Yun.

192
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,000
My father raised me as a boy.

193
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:33,520
He said only a boy could take his place

194
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,720
and perform on stage.

195
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:36,360
Now he's dead.

196
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,040
Girls can perform on stage.

197
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:40,360
But I can never change back.

198
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,800
I won't say anything.

199
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,680
I swear.

200
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:43,960
If you don't want me to say it,

201
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,240
I'll never say it.

202
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,520
Sister Yun.

203
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,040
Boss Yun.

204
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:53,720
Boss Jin.

205
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:55,520
Boss Yun.

206
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:56,600
Boss Jin.

207
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:01,080
Later, men and women could perform together.

208
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:03,160
The two troupes merged into one.

209
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,440
We were still inseparable.

210
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:08,250
Gossip was inevitable.

211
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,260
But we weren't afraid.

212
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:12,080
Only we knew.

213
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:14,140
She and I were confidants,

214
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,200
sworn sisters.

215
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:20,480
She didn't want to talk about it,

216
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,330
so I kept her secret all my life.

217
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:25,680
But since she had already acknowledged

218
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:27,010
the child in your belly,

219
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:30,220
why did you still leave the Yunshang Troupe?

220
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,970
I was always the troublemaker.

221
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,960
She had done enough for me.

222
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:38,920
She wanted me to hold my head high.

223
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,160
But if we stayed,

224
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:45,180
we would only be her weakness.

225
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:47,880
You kept her secret for half a lifetime.

226
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:50,100
Now that it's been exposed like this,

227
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:52,360
you must hate Xiaotangchun.

228
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:53,600
I hate her.

229
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,850
Of course I hate her.

230
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:58,330
I hate that I didn't kill her myself

231
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,200
and failed to avenge Boss Yun.

232
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:02,880
You know Xiaotangchun killed Boss Yun.

233
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,380
The night Boss Yun was killed,

234
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:08,600
I was there.

235
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:11,040
Are you still performing

236
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:12,920
today?

237
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:23,840
Come out.

238
00:12:30,640 --> 00:12:32,120
Why are you dressed like that?

239
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,040
Copying me?

240
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:35,360
There are reporters at the door.

241
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,720
If I'm recognized,

242
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,120
it'll ruin your show.

243
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,800
Once I take the stage,

244
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:43,580
you and Fengming are in for it.

245
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:45,520
Are you sure?

246
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,480
Man or woman,

247
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:50,720
Boss Yun,

248
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,050
you're the only one.

249
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:56,090
You protected us as a man

250
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:57,720
for half a lifetime.

251
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,800
From now on,

252
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,640
I'll keep you safe.

253
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,450
Sing without worry.

254
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,400
Finish this show.

255
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:22,560
I'll walk out with you, head held high.

256
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:29,840
Let's go.

257
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:30,760
Boss Jin.

258
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,480
Boss Yun.

259
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:45,680
How about...

260
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,400
...today...

261
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,280
we don't sing?

262
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,160
I'm not afraid.

263
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,380
What are you afraid of?

264
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:55,440
Are you afraid that once I take the stage,

265
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:57,570
you won't get the chance to replace me?

266
00:13:58,400 --> 00:14:01,060
Or are you afraid I'll expose your dirty secrets

267
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:04,240
right here on the stage?

268
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,280
Boss Yun.

269
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,880
I trust your integrity.

270
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:16,160
I kept you by my side all these years,

271
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:19,000
not to promote you,

272
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:20,840
but to keep an eye on you,

273
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:23,460
so you wouldn't harm anyone else.

274
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,720
But today I realized

275
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:28,290
that you will never change.

276
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:33,520
That's why you'll never be a star.

277
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:35,360
You never were,

278
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,720
and you never will be.

279
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:39,700
Finish today's performance,

280
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:41,600
then don't come back.

281
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,040
Boss Yun.

282
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:47,040
I don't know what you're talking about.

283
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:48,900
All I care about is singing opera.

284
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,760
If you won't let me sing,

285
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,800
I'd rather die.

286
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,320
Fine.

287
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,520
I'll grant your wish.

288
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:13,000
No need.

289
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:19,280
We'll sing it this way today.

290
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:21,040
Okay.

291
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,680
Okay.

292
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:29,840
Miss,

293
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:31,520
no one is here.

294
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:33,560
Come out.

295
00:16:08,560 --> 00:16:10,440
Boss Yun left a suicide note.

296
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,520
You knew it was Xiao Tangchun,

297
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:37,490
so why didn't you report it?

298
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:40,620
I can't prove that I'm telling the truth.

299
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:43,960
In this world,

300
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,000
truth and lies,

301
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:48,770
black and white, are hard to distinguish.

302
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:53,640
Whether Boss Yun is dead or alive,

303
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:55,100
we will find out the truth.

304
00:17:01,640 --> 00:17:02,770
By the way, Boss Jin,

305
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:05,690
at 9:00 a.m. the day before yesterday,

306
00:17:05,839 --> 00:17:06,760
where were you?

307
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,640
Fengming had a morning show that day.

308
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:11,700
It started at 8:00.

309
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:14,130
After the show, I went to help her pack.

310
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:15,880
Pack?

311
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:18,050
Was she going on a long trip?

312
00:17:18,319 --> 00:17:19,920
I wanted her to go to Beiping.

313
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:21,680
Leaving here

314
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:23,440
might be better for her.

315
00:17:25,520 --> 00:17:27,520
Sorry to bother you today, Boss Jin.

316
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:28,680
In the coming days,

317
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:30,940
we might come back to question you again.

318
00:17:31,360 --> 00:17:33,120
Please do not leave Shanghai.

319
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:37,200
If Boss Yun isn't dead,

320
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:39,420
then Jin Guizhi and Yun Feiyan

321
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:41,280
likely conspired together.

322
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:43,920
But if they conspired together,

323
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:45,640
why would she tell us this?

324
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:47,960
The more we know,

325
00:17:48,080 --> 00:17:49,640
the more likely we are to suspect her,

326
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:50,160
right?

327
00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:22,320
That person just now was Yun Feiyan.

328
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:46,040
She is not Yun Feiyan.

329
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:48,400
But I clearly saw her.

330
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,440
What's wrong?

331
00:19:06,320 --> 00:19:07,440
Seeing you,

332
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,800
What about seeing me?

333
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:17,920
Makes me want to puke.
